Procedure SoulCheck

Put "u soul"
    Waitfor "Sorry, but you don't seem to have one.","Sorry, that object cannot be used in that manner.",2
     Switch Found                              
      Case 1 : Soul = Soul + 1
               Delay 8  
               If Soul = 6
                GetOut "No Soulstone!"
               EndIf  
               Soulcheck
      Case 2 : Print "Soulstone still here!" 
                      Soul = 0
     EndSwitch 

EndProc
