Procedure Retreat
           
Repeat

 Put "sw"
 Waitfor "Sorry, you'll have to rest a while before you can move.","You must rest a moment before proceeding!","plaza.","in the heat",2
  Switch Found
   Case 1 : Zaryn
            Obiheal
   Case 2 : Delay 1
            Retreat
   Case 3 : Leavekusa                                       
   Case 4 : Zaryn
            Obiheal
  EndSwitch

Until Found

EndProc                
